extends baseEmail 

block content 
  p Hi and welcome to Eco-School project.
  p A new user account for you has been created to access the Owly application. To fully register your account we will need you to create a password.
  p (After you received this email the link will be valid for 5 days)
  p You can use POST method for url: #{url} with password and passwordConfirm as body or press the button below
  table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
    tbody
      tr
        td(align='left')
          table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
            tbody
              tr
                td
                  a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') Create your password
  p - Owly team